title: Je Tieng 1
description: A vegetarian restaurant that also sells frozen and dried mock meats and other vegetarian cooking ingredients. Restaurant serves buffet style dishes that change daily with vegan options; no food left after 12pm. Best time to arrive is in the early morning around 7am, though it will be crowded. There are a la carte dishes available until late afternoon. Je Tieng 2 is just 100 meters down the road and specializes in vegetarian hot pot (suki). No English spoken or written.
